Glovo is the #1 app for ordering anything you want! With more than 240,000 restaurants & stores available, and delivery in minutes. Download the app now & order a Glovo!

Easily order food, groceries and gifts in your city without leaving home.

Want to order food straight to your door? Or get a grocery delivery of your essentials? We save you time, when you don’t have it. 

WHY USE GLOVO?

▶ Over 80 million downloads worldwide.
▶ Order in 23 countries including Spain, Portugal, Romania, Morocco, Italy, Poland, Croatia, Ukraine, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Tunisia, Kenya, Uganda, Ivory Coast, Nigeria, Bulgaria, Serbia, Armenia, Bosnia-herzegovina, Montenegro, Moldova & Andorra.
▶ More than 240,000 restaurants, supermarkets and stores available globally.
▶ Deliveries from the biggest chains: McDonald's, Burger King, KFC, Pizza Hut, Taco Bell, Telepizza, Starbucks, Domino’s Pizza, Carrefour, PENNY., Eataly, Flying Tiger, Kiko Milano, Lafarmacia, Auchan, Decathlon, MediaMarkt and many more.

▶ Pay however you like. We accept PayPal, card payment, cash and even restaurant vouchers.
▶ Track your delivery or takeaway in real time and chat with our support team if need be.
▶ Subscribe to Glovo Prime and get unlimited free deliveries of food, groceries, and shopping. Save on every delivery! Available in selected countries.
▶ Invite your friends and earn money for each one who places an order on the app.

YOUR FAVOURITE FOOD, IN MINUTES!

Fancy a tasty dinner? Has it been a long day? You deserve to have your food delivered to your door! Or are you on your way somewhere? You can order food to take away and grab it on the go.

With Glovo, you can order up to 65 different types of food in your city. Including a burger from the most famous restaurants, to ordering from your favourite sushi place. There are more than 216,000 restaurants available worldwide for delivery or takeaway of your favourite food, in a matter of minutes.


GROCERY DELIVERY WITHOUT LEAVING HOME

Forget something from the supermarket? Got friends over and want to order another round of drinks or snacks? 

Now you can also order your groceries from the supermarket. Choose whatever you want from your favourite supermarket or local store and Glovo will deliver it to you in a few minutes. Food, snacks, drinks, something sweet, a missing ingredient... any groceries you need! 


THE APP TO ORDER ANYTHING

Glovo delivers everything. Find more than 27000 stores on the app, with all kinds of products. All your shopping on one app: surprise gifts, a last-minute purchase or whatever you need.

And if you need to send or pick up something in your city, Glovo can run errands for you. Choose a pick-up and delivery point and a courier will take care of the rest, with delivery in minutes!


NEED HELP? CONTACT US

If you’re looking for help with an order or have any questions about Glovo, please contact our support team via the support section in our app or on our website.

Breathing is one of the simplest ways to restore balance, and research shows that structured breathing practices can lower stress, improve focus, and support emotional stability. This app turns those techniques into easy daily routines that fit into real life.

On the home screen, you will see your icon, nickname, and a clear progress indicator. From here you can access breathing practices, daily tasks, your profile, app info, and settings. A statistics window lets you review your activity and see how consistent you have been.

The breathing section includes four guided methods:
• Abdominal breathing, proven to lower nervous system activity, helps reduce anxiety and return the body to a resting state.
• Rhythmic breathing balances internal pace, with short pauses after inhale and exhale that signal the body to slow down.
• Expansive breathing creates a sense of lightness by filling the chest and abdomen before releasing tension with a longer exhale.
• Releasing breath uses short inhales and extended exhales to quickly reduce irritation and emotional overload.

Each technique comes with step-by-step instructions, timing counts, and suggestions on when to use it whether before sleep, during moments of distraction, or in times of stress.

Daily tasks keep practice consistent without being repetitive. You may be asked to spend five minutes with abdominal breathing in the morning, try rhythmic cycles during a break, or combine expansive breathing with gentle stretches. At the end of the month, you can complete a “breathing session” that blends all four methods in sequence.

Your profile tracks either time or repetitions, depending on your preference. You can upload a photo, edit your nickname, and view personal analytics. Notifications, sound, and vibration can be adjusted in settings. An information section provides context on mental health and why breathing techniques are an evidence-based way to restore balance.

This is not just about exercises it is about creating a toolkit you can return to whenever you need clarity, calm, or energy. Each short session adds up, helping you build a reliable rhythm of stability throughout your day.

Club Plus Loyalty program je program nagrađivanja u koji će biti uključeno više partnera i svaki od njih Vas nagrađuje za kupovinu. U Club Plus programu ste uvijek na dobitku, jer svakog dana imate mogućnost da kroz kupovinu u Aroma, City i Conto marketima sakupljate finansijski benefit.
Za svaku obavljenu kupovinu sakupljate novčani iznos i ukoliko pređete minimalno definisani prag pojedinačne kupovine, ostvarujete pravo na besplatu kupovinu u visini sakupljenog novčanog iznosa. 
Obračunski period traje od 01. januara do 31. decembra tekuće godine. Svi koji u jednom obračunskom periodu pređu definisani prag minimalnog iznosa računa, ostvaruju pravo na korišćenje sakupljenih finansijskih sredstava. Tako sakupljena novčana sredstva se mogu koristiti već prilikom naredne kupovine ili se mogu sakupljati do momenta odluke o iskorištenju istih. Mogu se koristiti u potpunosti ili parcijalno. Sva neiskorišćena sakupljena novčana sredstva se 01. januara naredne godine poništavaju i kreće novi obračunski period.
Club Plus kartica u okviru svog programa ima club namijenjen penzionerima i nudi dodatne povoljnosti kroz dodatni procentualni povrata finansiskih sredstava za novu kupovinu

Kupovine na osnovu sakupljenih novačnih sredstava Vam ne omogućavaju sakupljanje novog novčanog iznosa na kartici.
Korisnik Kartice može postati svaka punoljetna osoba sa prebivalištem u Crnoj Gori koja društvu Domaća Trgovina d.o.o. putem registracije, stavi na raspolaganje obavezne podatke popunjavajući pristupnicu za Club Plus Karticu u objektu Domaće trgovine ili putem mobilne aplikacije.
Domaća Trgovina d.o.o. Podgorica je pokretač programa benefita Club Plus Kartica i izdavač lične Club Plus Kartice za sve registrovane korisnike, koja ostaje u njenom vlasništvu. Aktuelna pravila su dostupna na internet stranici www.aromamarketi.me

PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries.

Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space.

Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates!

* HOW PURE WORKS?
Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing.

* IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN
Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe.  

* WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE
Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery.

* OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE
Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. 
Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. 

PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside.
Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions:

- If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.
- All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations.
- Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase.
- All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy
- Terms and conditions: https://pure.app/terms/

Циан — ведущий сервис в России для тех, кто ищет недвижимость для аренды или покупки. Здесь можно легко найти жилье на короткий или длительный срок, а также предложения по продаже квартир, домов и коммерческих объектов. 

Наш сервис предлагает широкий выбор жилья как в новостройках, так и на вторичном рынке, включая уникальные проекты квартир и детальные планировки. Все объявления проходят модерацию, что гарантирует их актуальность и достоверность.

Более 80 фильтров для удобного поиска квартир и домов
Ищите квартиры и дома для покупки или аренды с помощью интерактивной карты в приложении — просто выберите нужный район. Более 80 фильтров помогут найти подходящий вариант с учетом инфраструктуры и характеристик жилья. Фильтруйте по цене, количеству комнат и другим параметрам. Сохраняйте поиск и добавляйте понравившиеся объекты в избранное, чтобы не упустить выгодные предложения от собственников без скрытых комиссий.

Широкий выбор квартир в новостройках
Просто задайте параметры поиска: срок сдачи ЖК, этаж, площадь, наличие или отсутствие отделки, а также цену за всю квартиру или за квадратный метр. Если вы предпочитаете покупку от застройщиков или вам важна комнатность вашей квартиры, для вас доступны специальные фильтры. Таким образом, вы сможете легко найти свой идеальный ЖК.

Умный Циан-помощник для поиска недвижимости
Циан-помощник — интеллектуальный сервис, который покажет подходящие варианты, поможет с ипотекой, сообщит о новых объявлениях, сэкономит время и поможет принять решение. Поручите поиск жилья искусственному интеллекту — задавайте критерии, а помощник пришлет вам подходящие варианты.

Оформление ипотеки
Заполните одну анкету и отправьте её сразу в 7 банков — всего за 2 минуты вы получите персональные предложения по ипотеке. Сравните условия и выберите то, что подходит именно вам. Ипотека — это первый шаг к вашему будущему дому или квартире. Начните путь к мечте уже сегодня!

Посуточная аренда квартир, домов и коттеджей
Удобный поиск жилья для посуточной аренды — квартиры, дома, коттеджи и комнаты. Смотрите варианты на карте или в списке, фильтруйте по цене, району, типу и удобствам. Легко сравнивайте объекты и выбирайте лучшее - в центре, у метро, у моря или рядом с достопримечательностями.

Размещение объявлений о сдаче и продаже недвижимости
Размещайте объявления о продаже или аренде недвижимости любого типа. В личном кабинете доступны инструменты для общения с покупателями и арендаторами — звонки, чат и поддержка агентов, которые помогут на всех этапах сделки.

Поиск коммерческой недвижимости для вашего бизнеса
Арендуйте или покупайте коммерческую недвижимость, подходящую под все ваши бизнес-потребности, включая офисы, склады, и торговые помещения. Удобные фильтры помогут быстро найти подходящий вариант по нужным параметрам. Сервис предоставляет широкий выбор предложений под разные цели и бюджеты.

Быстрая и бесплатная оценка недвижимости
Узнайте рыночную цену квартиры, дома или другой недвижимости быстро и бесплатно. Получите данные о кадастровой стоимости, текущих арендных ставках и истории цен по интересующему объекту. Это поможет точно оценить стоимость, выгодно инвестировать и принять обоснованное решение при продаже, покупке или аренде.

Если недвижимость, то Циан!

The DMSS app can enhance your security management efficiency. You can watch real-time surveillance videos and play them back anytime, anywhere, via Wi-Fi or cellular networks. If a device alarm is triggered, DMSS will immediately push an instant notification to you.

DMSS offers：
1. Real-time Live View：
You can view real-time surveillance videos from the added devices anytime, anywhere, to help you better monitor the safety of your home environment.

2. Video Playback：
You can quickly find the events you care about by date and event category, and playback the required historical video footage.

3. Instant Alarm Notifications：
You can subscribe to different alarm events according to your needs.  When an event is triggered, you will immediately receive the message notification.

4. Device Sharing
You can share the device with family members for shared use and assign them different usage permissions.

5. Alarm Hub
You can add a variety of peripheral accessories to the alarm hub to provide warnings for potential theft, intrusion, fire, water damage, and other situations. In case of an unforeseen event, DMSS can immediately activate alarms and send out danger notifications.

6. Visual Intercom
You can add visual intercom devices to engage in video calls between the device and the DMSS, as well as perform functions like locking and unlocking.

7. Access Control
You can add access control devices to check the current status of doors and view unlock records, as well as perform remote unlocking operations on the doors.
